<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-83-0782 </DOCNO><TEXT>The demand for storage in supercomputer environments is increasing andforcing an evolution toward distributed storage systems. In this paper,I will describe some existing storage systems and some requirements forfuture systems. I will also describe the Storage Reference Model beingdeveloped by the IEEE Computer Society and a new storage system beingdeveloped at Livermore according to the IEEE model. 12 refs., 6 figs.</TEXT></DOC>